I bought this DVD set when I noticed it came with the ultraviolet digital copy. The movies themselves are cute and fun for the whole family, but please be aware that the digital copy for the set is not for all four movies as I assumed it was. The UV code is only for 'Scared Silly' so I just wanted to let potential buyers know to help avoid being disappointed like I was when I discovered this. It's a good little bundle however if your only interested in the DVD's with Open Season/Open Season 2 on disc one & Open Season 3/Open Season: Scared Silly on disc two. All are Rated PG, mostly for having mild rude humor and some action.
